'''Battle of [[Balmorra/Legends|Balmorra]]''' can refer to:

*The [[Battle of Balmorra (Galactic Wars)|ongoing battle]] that lasted during the [[Great Galactic War]] and [[Cold War (Galactic Republic&ndash;Sith Empire)|Cold War]].
*The [[Battle of Balmorra (Clone Wars)|battle]] prior to the [[Outer Rim Sieges/Legends|Outer Rim Sieges]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]
*A [[Raid on Balmorra|raid]] by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].
*The [[Battle of Balmorra]] during the Galactic Civil War.
*The [[Second Battle of Balmorra|battle]] during the [[Second Galactic Civil War]].

